list-style:none;zoom:1;width:775px;\">\r\n					</ul>\r\n					<div class=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;word-break:break-all;\">\r\n						三亚海韵度假酒店“醉爱海韵-情侣档” &nbsp;豪华海景房&nbsp;<br />\r\n房间面积41-47㎡，可住2人，该房型不可加床（部分房间带有贵妃榻：1m宽*2m长，可代替加床）&nbsp;<br />\r\n楼层分布：大床6-16层、双床6-11层&nbsp;<br />\r\n床型分布：大床2m宽*2m长，双床1.35m宽*2m长。&nbsp;<br />\r\n该房型可安排无烟楼层、可做无烟处理，宽带有线/无线（免费）。&nbsp;<br />\r\n侧面观海，所有房间带阳台，部分房间阳台带浴缸。\r\n					</div>\r\n					<ul class=\"cf\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;zoom:1;width:775px;\">\r\n						<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;float:left;\">\r\n							<img data-original=\"https://imgs.qunarzz.com/p/tts8/1610/60/679a1d2f9cb90502.jpg_r_750x2022x90_bf584d14.jpg\" class=\"other-custom lazy-load-img\" src=\"https://imgs.qunarzz.com/p/tts8/1610/60/679a1d2f9cb90502.jpg_r_750x2022x90_bf584d14.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:bottom;overflow:hidden;margin:0px 4px 0px 0px;width:750px;height:auto;display:inline;\" /> \r\n						</li>\r\n						<li style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;float:left;\">\r\n							<div class=\"g_tel\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top;font-size:0px;\">\r\n								<div class=\"g_tel_box\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;text-size-adjust:100%;position:relative;display:inline-block;\">\r\n									<img data-original=\"https://imgs.qunarzz.com/p/tts6/1610/b7/ddfe1a4902850f02.jpg_r_750x2278x90_99a34821.jpg\" class=\"other-custom lazy-load-img\" src=\"https://imgs.qunarzz.com/p/tts6/1610/b7/ddfe1a4902850f02.jpg_r_750x2278x90_99a34821.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:bottom;overflow:hidden;margin:0px 4px 10px 0px;width:750px;height:auto;display:inline;\" /> \r\n									<div class=\"g_tel_num13 g_tel_l\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;position:absolute;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.498039);left:0px;bottom:10px;\">\r\n										<div class=\"num_ct\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:10px 12px 8px;float:left;\">\r\n											<p style=\"margin-top:0px;marg