0px 22px;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:28px;\">可选酒店<var style=\"font-style:normal;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial;margin-left:3px;\">1</var></strong> \r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"product-c-detail clrfix unfold-img-area\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px;zoom:1;\">\r\n							<span class=\"product-img\" style=\"float:left;\"><img src=\"https://imgs.qunarzz.com/p/tts1/1606/f8/8772dc789b15d9f7.jpg_r_440x293x90_58cf2fa0.jpg\" class=\"other-middlepic lazy-load-img\" style=\"vertical-align:bottom;width:240px;height:160px;overflow:hidden;\" /></span> \r\n							<div class=\"product-text\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 15px;float:left;width:497px;height:160px;position:relative;\">\r\n								<div class=\"title\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 5px;border-bottom:0px;position:relative;\">\r\n									<strong style=\"font-size:18px;\">三亚海韵度假酒店（Ocean Sonic Resort Sanya）</strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"scenic\" style=\"top:-2px;margin-left:10px;height:19px;line-height:19px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;border-radius:2px;padding:0px 5px;background:#FFA726;color:#FFFFFF;position:relative;\"><span class=\"scenic-ico\" style=\"width:3px;height:5px;position:absolute;top:6px;left:-3px;background:url(&quot;\"></span>豪华型</span> \r\n								</div>\r\n								<div class=\"location\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#999999;width:600px;\">\r\n									三亚市三亚湾路168号&nbsp;<a class=\"map examine-map\" style=\"color:#0084BB;margin-left:10px;vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block;\"><span class=\"map-ico\" style=\"width:10px;height:14px;margin-left:4px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;background-image:url(&quot;background-position:0px -219px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;overflow:hidden;margin-right:5px;\"></span>查看地图</a> \r\n								</div>\r\n								<div class=\"hotel-score clrfix\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 15px;zoom:1;position:absolute;left:0px;bottom:0px;\">\r\n									<div id=\"sanya_37330_comment\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n										<div class=\"score\" style=\"margin:0px 10px 0px 0px;padding:0px;float:left;font-size:14px;width:64px;height:54px;line-height:54px;background:#F2F2F2;text-align:center;\">\r\n											<var style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;\">4.7</var>/5分\r\n										</div>\r\n										<div class=\"assess\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 74px;padding:0px;height:54px;\">\r\n											<div class=\"swiper-container swiper-container-vertical\" id=\"comment-swiper-container\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:56px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;z-index:1;width:419px;\">\r\n												<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;position:absolute;top:-69px;width:419px;\">\r\n													<div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:69px;\">\r\n														<ul style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">\r\n															<li class=\"hotel-comment\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:24px;line-height:24px;vertical-align:middle;\">\r\n																<span class=\"l-quotes\" style=\"position:relative;top:-2px;display:inline-block;width:12px;height:9px;overflow:hidden;background-image:url(&quot;background-position:-18px -160px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;margin-right:2px;\"></span><span data-content=\"环境好服务也很好，下次来还会选择海韵，前台陈岩岩态度很好人也很美！\" style=\"color:#999999;font-size:14px;height:24px;display:inline-block;line-height:36px;overflow:hidden;max-width:382px;\">环境好服务也很好,下次来还会选择海韵</span><span class=\"r-quotes\" style=\"position:relative;top:-2px;display:inline-block;width:12px;height:9px;overflow:hidden;background-image:url(&quot;background-position:-31px -160px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;margin-left:2px;\"></span> \r\n															</li>\r\n														</ul>\r\n														<ul style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">\r\n															<li class=\"hotel-comment\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:24px;line-height:24px;vertical-align:middle;\">\r\n																<span class=\"l-quotes\" style=\"position:relative;top:-2px;display:inline-block;width:12px;height:9px;overflow:hidden;background-image:url(&quot;background-position:-18px -160px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;margin-right:2px;\"></span><span data-content=\"海韵酒店在当地很有名，出租车司机都知道。酒店位于三亚湾海边，从酒店可以直接看到海边。酒店装饰很有特点，酒店公共区域随处可见的热带植物和花卉，还有很多供客人休息的沙发，凳子和小床，真的床。酒店的游泳池很大，水浅大约是为了小孩的安全着想。有一些简单的水上设施供小孩和大人玩耍。还配有温水池，这点值得点赞。还有一些简单的类似小区里的健身器材。 选择的高级海景房，从阳台看出去大约45度的海景，感觉很不错。尤其是早晚可以坐在阳台上欣赏海景和酒店夜景。和很多三亚的酒店一样，在阳台里放了一个小型浴缸，并对外有帘子遮挡，不过实用性不大。一是隐私问题；二是还因为是在室外，海边风大，总有些灰尘，不太愿意每次使用前还要清洗。 房间里的设施也比较齐，常见的一应俱全。咖啡杯，红酒杯都有。房间采光很好，灯光设置也很齐全，壁柜灯，床头阅读灯，台灯，夜灯，阳台灯都有。晚上房间开灯后亮度基本满意。房间服务业比较到位，打扫卫生很快，出去吃个早餐的空隙，服务员就把房间整理好了。为了喝红酒，向酒店要了个开瓶器，也立即送到了房间。因为一家子住，衣服较多，服务员在整理房间后发现这个问题，主动多留了几个衣架，并留了字条，给人温馨的感觉。 说说瑕疵。阳台灯有点小问题，会闪烁，亮度不够。淋浴器大的喷头有些堵，喷水有些问题。卫生间放卷筒纸的架子设计不合理，取用纸的时候很容易把纸弄掉。 客房楼 大堂 阳台观海 酒店大堂外 房间\" style=\"color:#999999;font-size:14px;height:24px;display:inline-block;line-height:36px;overflow:hidden;max-width:382px;\">酒店装饰很有特点</span><span class=\"r-quotes\" style=\"position:relative;top:-2px;display:inline-block;width:12px;height:9px;overflow:hidden;background-image:url(&quot;background-position:-31px -160px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;margin-left:2px;\"></span> \r\n															</li>\r\n														</ul>\r\n													</div>\r\n													<div class=\"swiper-slide\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;height:69px;\">\r\n														<ul style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;\">\r\n															<li class=\"hotel-comment\" style=\