(16, 1, 6, 5, '0,5,', -1, -1, '', '海口--怀旧路线攻略', '', '', 'h', '携程', 'admin', '', '', '', '<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	怀旧路线（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/haikou37/52006.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2828858_37_sid52006_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"52006\" data-id=\"10524172\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color:#0086B4;text-decoration:none;outline:none;border-bottom:1px dotted #0086B4;padding-bottom:2px;\">骑楼老街</a>→骑楼小吃街→冯小刚电影公社）\r\n	</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	博爱北路→解放西路→大同路→龙华路→龙昆北路→龙昆南路→迎宾大道→羊山大道→冯小刚电影公社，车程约15公里，28分钟。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	美丽的“椰城”<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag place\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/haikou37.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2828858_37_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"37\" data-id=\"36\" data-type=\"4\" style=\"color:#0086B4;text-decoration:none;outline:none;border-bottom:1px dotted #0086B4;padding-bottom:2px;\">海口</a>，一切浪漫风光，动人景致，都与时间有着千丝万缕的牵绊。海口到处镌刻着时间的记忆，骑楼老街上斑驳的印记，<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/haikou37/51610.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2828858_37_sid51610_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"51610\" data-id=\"83990\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color:#0086B4;text-decoration:none;outline:none;border-bottom:1px dotted #0086B4;padding-bottom:2px;\">海口钟楼</a>那未曾停下的指针，不知走过了多少岁月；<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi locale hotspot_tag sight\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/haikou37/3172.html#ctm_ref=gs_290602_2828858_37_sid3172_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-resourceid=\"3172\" data-id=\"75943\" data-type=\"3\" style=\"color:#0086B4;text-decoration:none;outline:none;border-bottom:1px dotted #0086B4;padding-bottom:2px;\">五公祠</a>隐没在城市清幽之处，诉说着海南历史文化及具有海南特色的古代建筑艺术的文物古迹；用时间书写着历史的痕迹。\r\n	</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65086905\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65086905|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65086905\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65086905|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M03/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyeAJLm6AAIo6qqvp4o617_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M03/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyeAJLm6AAIo6qqvp4o617_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M03/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyeAJLm6AAIo6qqvp4o617_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"894\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n		</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	从现在回看百年前的海口，是一个什么心情的穿越？要有多少斑驳，时光才会入墙。\r\n			</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65086951\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65086951|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65086951\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65086951|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/8D/44/CggYr1a_PyiAXeGGAAV58Pj5HHk889_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/8D/44/CggYr1a_PyiAXeGGAAV58Pj5HHk889_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/8D/44/CggYr1a_PyiAXeGGAAV58Pj5HHk889_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"503\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n				</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	俗话说：进一座城，就要先了解一座城市的历史。坐落在水巷口的海口南洋骑楼老街风貌展示馆，就是这样一个展示老街历史的场馆。水巷口曾是琼州府的官渡和繁忙热闹的码头，来往海口的南洋客和商家民众都从这里乘船出海或登岸返回。而今，这里是旅游集散广场，也是游客进入老街的第一站，在这里您将首先了解到海口骑楼老街的历史。\r\n					</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65086996\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65086996|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65086996\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65086996|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M0B/8B/CC/CggYtFa_PyiAPe-NAAKy0FmduPM945_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M0B/8B/CC/CggYtFa_PyiAPe-NAAKy0FmduPM945_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M0B/8B/CC/CggYtFa_PyiAPe-NAAKy0FmduPM945_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"503\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n						</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	海口骑楼老街，是海口市一处最具特色的街道景观。其中最古老的建筑四牌楼建于南宋，至今有700多年历史。\r\n							</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65087433\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65087433|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65087433\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65087433|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M08/87/85/CggYGla_PymAUdrJAAOaqkM3Kbs578_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M08/87/85/CggYGla_PymAUdrJAAOaqkM3Kbs578_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M08/87/85/CggYGla_PymAUdrJAAOaqkM3Kbs578_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"671\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n								</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	骑楼建筑最早见于2000多年前的古希腊，近代才流行于南欧及地中海一带，并传至东南亚。海口得胜沙路、文明东路、中山路、博爱路、解放路，两侧都是一幢幢始建于十九世纪末的南洋风格柱廊式骑楼。\r\n									</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65087147\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65087147|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65087147\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65087147|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/A1/81/CggYGVa_PyqAENgYAANmmHc63_k092_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/A1/81/CggYGVa_PyqAENgYAANmmHc63_k092_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/A1/81/CggYGVa_PyqAENgYAANmmHc63_k092_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"671\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n										</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	骑楼老街是非常古老的一条街，街边是民国时代风格的建筑，当地人总是在傍晚和晚上聚在一起喝茶聊天，其乐融融，甚至还有小时候才见过的那种戏台子呢。\r\n											</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65086998\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65086998|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65086998\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65086998|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M00/8B/D0/CggYsla_PyuAQ3-nAAFG2Xwltxw547_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M00/8B/D0/CggYsla_PyuAQ3-nAAFG2Xwltxw547_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg07.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g6/M00/8B/D0/CggYsla_PyuAQ3-nAAFG2Xwltxw547_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"671\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n												</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	据说上个世纪二三十年代，一股闯南洋风潮在海南刮开，在异乡打出一片天地后，出海闯南洋的海南人“叶落归根”，携带着毕生血汗钱回乡建屋，安老终生。祖辈们在带回了南洋思想的同时，借鉴南洋建筑的装饰风格，融合中国传统文化创造出的一种多元化的建筑，这些骑楼今天仍在使用，主要分布于海口市得胜沙路、中山路、博爱路、新华路、解放路、长堤路等老街区。\r\n													</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65086715\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65086715|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65086715\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65086715|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M00/8D/45/CggYr1a_PyuAQV1QAARIkJyaNOs330_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M00/8D/45/CggYr1a_PyuAQV1QAARIkJyaNOs330_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M00/8D/45/CggYr1a_PyuAQV1QAARIkJyaNOs330_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"671\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.gif?t=\"127ae5a836800c9d6e9b2b8aee9439e5&quot;&quot;\"></a> \r\n														</div>\r\n<br style=\"color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:32px;word-break:break-all;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, \" white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\">\r\n	骑楼老街覆盖面积约二平方公里，总长四点四公里，共有大大小小的三、四层高的骑楼建筑近六百栋。走进骑楼老街区，就像是时代突然倒退了几十年一样，好像回到小时候每天放学必经的“同仁街”。\r\n															</p>\r\n<div id=\"img65087052\" class=\"img\" data-likeid=\"65087052|2828858\" data-likecategory=\"1\" data-shareid=\"65087052\" data-sharecategory=\"1\" data-referenceids=\"65087052|50643558\" data-referencecategory=\"1\" style=\"background-image:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" ctd_img_bg.png?t=\"f66e6c7e79c4a01fc72dcea1cd02e424&quot;margin:30px\" 0px=\"\" 10px;position:relative;z-index:1;width:790px;overflow:hidden;color:#333333;font-family:arial,=\"\" \"font-size:16px;white-space:normal;background-color:#ffffff;\"=\"\"> <a target=\"_blank\" share-pic=\"1\" title=\"点击查看原图\" href=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyyAUJiMAAMiAUyvI5o913_R_1024_10000_Q90.jpg\" style=\"color:#00A7E1;text-decoration:none;outline:none;\"><img class=\"lary_1\" data-original=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyyAUJiMAAMiAUyvI5o913_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" src=\"https://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/9F/A5/CggYG1a_PyyAUJiMAAMiAUyvI5o913_C_671_10000_Q90.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"671\" style=\"display:block;max-width:670px;overflow:hidden;margin:0px auto;background:url(\" http:=\"\" pages.c-ctrip.com=\"\" gs_static=\"\" travels=\"\" img=\"\" img_loading.